data.description: Your search is over! This captivating 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom split-level ranch is found in the Linden Gardens development.  Step from the Welcome mat into an interior embrace that includes hardwoods in the bedrooms and living spaces, stylish lighting, neutral decor, and two wood burning fireplaces (living room). The kitchen promises many-a-great meal, with fresh updates and premium appliances. Restful primary bedroom. The other two bedrooms are ready for your decorative expertise. Unfinished basement. Attached one-car garage. Enjoy grilling on the good-as-new wood deck. Open the front door to a pleasant new life here in Columbus
